    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Put a large baking tray (or two!) in the oven to heat up (this will stop your pizza bottoms from going soggy!)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain and pat your <strong>mozzarella</strong> dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!)</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>to a small bowl with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and stir it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>tomato base</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza base[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>tomato base</strong> between the <strong>pizza base[s] </strong>and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong>, your <strong>pepperoni</strong> and the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2 or more? Make sure the pizzas don't overlap on the tray to avoid raw dough!</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 13-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the base is crisp \u2013 this is your <strong>double cheese pepperoni pizza</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/double-cheese-pepperoni-pizza-with-garlic-and-herb-dip/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>double cheese</strong> <strong>pepperoni pizza</strong> with the<strong> garlic & herb dip </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
